OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779642355
OL,3,CThe PM's miserable month and
OL,4,CStormont's TACOs
OL,6,FIn the end, Labour had a catastrophic
OL,7,Fnight - losing over 1,000 councillors
OL,8,Fin England, losing yet more ground in
OL,9,FScotland, and suffering defeat in
OL,10,FWales for the first time in a century.
OL,12,FThe fallout has been immense.
OL,14,FAt the time of writing, one cabinet
OL,15,Fminister, four junior ministers, and
OL,16,Ffour ministerial aides have resigned
OL,17,Fin protest. Over 95 of Starmer's own
OL,18,FMPs have called for him to go.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
