OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779642355
OL,3,CThe PM's miserable month and
OL,4,CStormont's TACOs
OL,6,FMayor of Greater Manchester and
OL,7,FStarmer nemesis Andy Burnham announced
OL,8,Fhis intention to stand in the by-
OL,9,Felection for Makerfield, triggered by
OL,10,FJosh Simons' resignation.
OL,12,FThe party's National Executive
OL,13,FCommittee - who had previously blocked
OL,14,Fhis candidacy when he applied to be
OL,15,Fits candidate in the Gorton and Denton
OL,16,Fby-election - made clear they would
OL,17,Fnot block his path.
OL,19,FThe poll is expected to be held on 18
OL,20,FJune.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
