PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779642355
OL,3,CThe PM's miserable month and
OL,4,CStormont's TACOs
OL,6,F"The Secretary of State, on behalf of
OL,7,Fthe Prime Minister, formally responded
OL,8,Fto the first and deputy first
OL,9,Fministers on April 28, and dialogue is
OL,10,Fongoing between the UK Government and
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland Executive.
OL,13,F"The UK Government has provided a
OL,14,F#19.3 billion per year on average
OL,15,Ffunding settlement for the spending
OL,16,Freview period, the largest in real-
OL,17,Fterms in the history of devolution.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
