OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779642355
OL,3,CThe PM's miserable month and
OL,4,CStormont's TACOs
OL,6,F"It is the responsibility of the
OL,7,FExecutive to manage that carefully. In
OL,8,Faddition to this, the Chancellor has
OL,9,Fannounced over #750 million additional
OL,10,Ffunding in Barnett consequentials."
OL,12,FAgainst that financial backdrop,
OL,13,Fministers, arms length bodies, and
OL,14,Funions have warned of the dire
OL,15,Fconsequences of the continued fiscal
OL,16,Flimbo.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
