OL,3,CThe PM's miserable month and
OL,4,CStormont's TACOs
OL,6,FIn the last week, the Education
OL,7,FMinister told UTV that three Stormont
OL,8,Fdepartments are in the red to the tune
OL,9,Fof #1.5bn, the BMA says some doctors
OL,10,Fwill strike next month in a dispute
OL,11,Fover pay, Translink has warned that
OL,12,Fservices could be reduced and fare
OL,13,Fdiscounts removed to cut costs, and
OL,14,FNIPSA told UTV its message to local
OL,15,Fpoliticians was to 'spend anyway' and
OL,16,F'burst their budgets' to avoid public
OL,17,Fsector strike action.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
