OL,3,CThe PM's miserable month and
OL,4,CStormont's TACOs
OL,6,FAnd so the stalemate continues. As the
OL,7,Fgame of chicken between Westminster
OL,8,Fand Stormont goes on, what happens
OL,9,Fnext will be determined by who blinks
OL,10,Ffirst.
OL,12,FIn this episode of UTV Talking
OL,13,FPolitics, Tracey and Vicki discuss the
OL,14,FPM's miserable May, our version of
OL,15,FTACO & the creep of Stormont suspicion.
OL,17,FListen here or watch on ITVX.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
